==Introduction==
The '''WikiModel''' element contains all Wiki model definitions and is stored in the '''model.xml''' file.

It allows to:
* record all changes made in the model over the time (in the structure and custom visualizations),
* define a domain specific data model to be managed in the Wiki
* and define a structure and content of the reports generated based on the data.


==Definition==

<pre>
<WikiModel xmlns="http://tide.act.nato.int/team/wat"
  name="{WIKI NAME}" image="{WIKI LOGO}" theme="{THEME}">
  <description>{WIKI DESCRIPTION}</description>
  <header>{WIKI HEADER}</header>

  <ChangeLog>{CHANGE LOG}</ChangeLog>
  <DataModel>{DATA MODEL}</DataModel>
  <ReportsModel>{REPORTS MODEL}</ReportsModel>
<WikiModel>
</pre>

{| class="helptable"
|-
! {WIKI NAME}
| A short name of the Wiki.
|-
! {WIKI LOGO}
| A name of image with the Wiki logo.
|-
! {THEME}
| A styling theme to be used to render Wiki pages. The following options are currently suppoeted:
* pluton
* mars
|-
! {WIKI DESCRIPTION}
| A long description of the Wiki.
|-
! {WIKI HEADER}
| A text displayed in a header of every Wiki page. Usually contains security markings applicable for Wiki instance.
|-
! {CHANGE LOG}
| A list of changes made in the model. See [[Help:Change Log|Change Log]] for more details.
|-
! {DATA MODEL}
| A domain specific data model to be managed in the Wiki. See [[Help:Data Model|Data Model]] for more details.
|-
! {REPORTS MODEL}
| A structure and content of the reports generated based on the data. See [[Help:Reports|Reports]] for more details.
|}


==Example==
<pre>
<WikiModel xmlns="http://tide.act.nato.int/team/wat" name="CIAV" version="1.0" image="CIAV.png">
  <description>The CIAV Wiki is the online information repository and tool for the Federated Mission Networking (FMN) Coalition Interoperability Assurance and Validation (CIAV) community.</description>

  <ChangeLog>...</ChangeLog>
  <DataModel>...</DataModel>
  <ReportsModel>...</ReportsModel>
<WikiModel>
</pre>


==User Interaface==
The content of the Wiki Model file is uploaded in the '''Project:Wiki Model''' page.
